data.description: Welcome to your tranquil retreat in San Marcos, nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac within the esteemed Rose Ranch neighborhood. This half-acre* property is a perfect blend of luxury living and an entertainer's dream, offering over 2,500 sqft of elegantly designed living space bathed in natural light.  As you enter, you're greeted by a layout meticulously tailored for contemporary lifestyles. The home boasts three spacious bedrooms, while a bonus room on the ground floor presents a flexible space, perfect as a home office, guest room, or creative studio. The kitchen, a chef's delight, features granite countertops, soft-close cabinetry, and high-end appliances.  The backyard of this property is a true highlight, having been the chosen venue for two weddings. It's an entertainer's haven with a solar-heated pool and a tranquil garden, offering a picturesque setting for gatherings or peaceful relaxation.  This home is ideally located near top-rated K-12 schools and is part of a community celebrated for its serene ambiance. Complementing its luxurious appeal, the property is equipped with 30 solar panels and a battery, enabling nearly off-grid living, and a Life Source Water System, marrying sustainability with modern comfort.  Discover the perfect fusion of luxury, functionality, and eco-conscious living in this versatile sanctuary. Embrace a lifestyle of sophistication and comfort at the heart of San Marcos, where every detail is crafted for an elevated living experience.
